Section: python
Priority: optional
Build-Depends: python3 (>= 3.6), debhelper (>= 11), dh-python
Standards-Version: 4.1.3
X-Python3-Version: >= 3.6

Package: indicator-ppa-download-statistics
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1, python3-gi, python3-notify2
Description:  Application indicator which displays PPA download statistics.
 A user can add any number of PPAs and the download counts will be retrieved.
 If a PPA contains a lot of packages, the user can filter the results to suit.
